        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Don't restart as Iksar your DE is fine.  You can try Oasis for a while more.  Then at like 18th I would try aviaks.  You could go sooner, but would be hard for a group.  Better money for you.  Stay there for a few levels at least.  Then in your 20's i highly recommend treants in SK and druids.  great cash and exper.  You can save up a few k plat then.</P><P>Evilzor Painmaker<BR>53rd on 7th hammer</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
