        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Also, at 14th level your Int doesn't provide that much extra mana. Try to get some +mana items.  According to the Mana calculator at Caster's Realm, 1 Int point nets you about 2 mana.  But if you pick up something like a +10 mana bracelet or a couple of Moonstone rings (+30 Mana each) that's a big boost.</P><P>Mana Calculator:</P><P><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/misc/manacalc/manacalc_int.asp" target="_blank">http://eq.castersrealm.com/misc/manacalc/manacalc_int.asp</a></P><P>Jewelry:</P><P><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/secrets/recipes_jewlcraft.htm" target="_blank">http://www.eqtraders.com/secrets/recipes_jewlcraft.htm</a></P><P>Gear Search:</P><P><a href="http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/itemsearch.html" target="_blank">http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/itemsearch.html</a></P><P>Loreana Shahnra<BR>Human Heretic of Innoruuk<BR>Tribunal</P><P>'And the Servants of Death wailed loudly and beat their breasts <BR>with their fists and cries of "No More" went unheard,<BR>for the gods cared not but for their gold.<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
