        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">The first hp to mana spell is Dark Pact.  Allure doesn't come until 20.</P><P>That aside, I'd suggest leaving Oasis, immediately, and heading for WC to hunt bears until the kodiaks go blue, then hit the Overthere until your low 20s.  WC and OT are both good experience, have much better loot than the gators in Oasis, and you don't have the risk of getting trained by spectres, sand giants, or whatever else some moron who's just learning to kite might dump on you.</P><P>Nilnayr Malignifex<BR>-Antonican Badass, Shadowhunter, citizen of E'ci<BR>an_obnoxious_twink_03 "I didn't know you could do that..."<BR>Me - "I'm a necromancer.  I can do anything.<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
